This paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as entity type tagging and proposes a new task of context-dependent fine type tagging. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). It also involves the use of knowledge bases and machine learning techniques, which are common in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of context and local information, which is relevant to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories.
